# ─── Architecture diagrams ───────────────────────────────
# PNGs / SVGs ship in the repo because they are the rendered
# images that docs/diagrams/*.md embeds via ``.. image::``
# directives — Pages needs them in the artifact. mmd / pdf /
# the maintainer's local regeneration script stay ignored.
docs/diagrams/*.mmd
docs/diagrams/*.pdf
docs/diagrams/render_diagrams.py

